&lt;li&gt;Manage BOM and inventory, performing regular cycle counts to ensure accurate part counts and inventory reconciliation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with production teams to fulfill material transfer requests and support manufacturing schedules.&lt;/li&gt;
